name: BEAUTIFUL BLIND
description:
how to find something that can't be found. then I realized the feel of a mournful body, silent and motionless saying I had found it.
 
"Yes I have found it!" said the surface skin shouted. 

"I say again, you have found it!" said the skin of the scales shouted back. 

"where?" 

"where?" 

like the whispering wind: "You've found it since you finished asking that question" 

The End.
